metadata.description: Bored Ape Seeks Yacht Club #1.  This ERC-721 token grants the holder access to read the full digital comic book for BASYC #1 at our website BoredApeSeeksYachtClub.com  Follow along with American Ape, inspired by BAYC #5636 as he travels through the metaverse in search of the legendary Bored Ape Yacht Club.  Now that he's officially a stranger in a strange land, will a case of mistaken identity lead American Ape to his demise at the hands of the Ape Mafia?
metadata.name: Bored Ape Seeks Yacht Club Issue #1
